				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					Re: Whistleblower reveals Big Pharma pressures researchers to only release &quot;positive&quot;
				</h2>
				

						
						
				<div class="content">
					<div id="post_message_1859469">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							This is why Ben Goldacre's <a href="http://opentrials.net/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Opentrials</a> project is so important. It's an initiative that is trying to to get all trials registered and then published. It has quite a number of pharma companies registered, but nowhere near all. None of this stuff is new - have a read of Ben Goldacre's 'Bad Pharma'.
						</blockquote>
