<br />
She now works for a small company in Delaware that among other things came up for a cure for a type of cancer that actually boosts the patient's immune system while they take it unlike your typical chemo therapies. In their short history that small company has brought ~3-4 new drugs online.<br />
<br />
I'm counting the days till some uber company makes the owners (it's an LLC afaik) an offer the <i>cannot refuse.</i>
